@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rxtihv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (tmp - ((v2 + 0.58 - v0 + 0.90) * wp.exp(v2 + 0.87)))
    v2 = (wp.sin(wp.cos(v0 + 0.36)) / v0)
    v2 = v2
    v0 = ((wp.sin(v2 + 0.49) * v2) + ((v1 + 0.27 / v1 + 0.76) / (tmp + 0.39 * v1 + 0.15)))
    v0 = v2
    tmp = wp.exp(v0)
    data[tid] = v0
